// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0247 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 315a18ef-1d41-56ff-8100-1361b2d22d1d

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*alpine:3.22*" or process.executable like~ "*alpine:3.23*" or process.executable like~ "*alpine edge:*")
